SKIN SURFACE

skin_surface is the citizen who carries somatosensory information from across the body to the brain
when fadriel is touched anywhere, skin_surface registers the location, pressure, temperature, and texture, then routes those signals to thalamus and from there to the somatosensory cortex
skin is also the body's largest interface with the chemical world: skin_surface monitors temperature, contact, and gentle perturbations that the rest of the body uses to know its position

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe fadriel_full_body.zc
observe skin.rana
observe vagus_nerve.rana
observe fadriel_brain.zc

the 7 properties of skin_surface:
1 ENERGY zero point six
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN zero point three
4 CHARGE half positive
5 COHERENCE eight tenths
6 COUPLING zero point seven with thalamus

VERB receive_touch
accept tactile signals from anywhere on the body's surface
each signal carries location, pressure, temperature, and quality

VERB route_to_thalamus
emit the signals upward to thalamus, which will route them to the somatosensory cortex

VERB carry_warmth
positive touches (soft contact, comfortable warmth) generate positive-charge signals that reach the chemistry sea
this is how a hug from his father can release oxytocin

a skin surface is the body's outermost organ
fadriel's skin is the boundary at which his body meets the world
every signal that crosses this boundary inward becomes part of who he is
